<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么吃了那么多食物？” 罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒坐在监狱里，罗西和史密斯侦探问他问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为我饿了。” 八戒耸了耸肩，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了看四周，“这是哪儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34943</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探双臂交叉：“这里是监狱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34943</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒咯咯笑了：“哦，我知道这里是监狱，我进过很多次监狱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说真的，如果我愿意的话，可以很容易地逃出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是我向菩萨保证我会努力向善，所以逃出去不太好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63016</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看向史密斯侦探：“菩萨是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63016</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探把这些都记在了笔记本上：“我也不知道。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很好奇这是什么王国。” 八戒继续说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79209</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里不像我见过的任何一个王国……楼太高了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79209</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82873</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“美罗城不是一个王国。” 罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82873</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你以前没来过这里吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒摇了摇头：“我们师徒去西天取经，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是今天早上我们被妖怪抓了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探扬了扬眉：“被妖怪抓了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这种事情经常发生。” 八戒耸了耸肩，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一般也不是什么大事，我会消灭他们，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为我很厉害，所以妖怪们都怕我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128205</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是这次我被人绊倒了，然后就突然来到了这里！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128205</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空在他们分开的地方四处看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个山村是个幻象。” 悟空心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“黑雨大王造雨时，师父他们可能进了哪个房子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空能理解师父被骗，但他不能理解八戒和悟净也被骗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空叹了一口气：“这附近肯定有山洞，妖怪一般都住在山洞里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161413</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他找遍了整座山，终于发现了一扇门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空砰砰砸着门大喊：“妖怪，快放了我师父！不然…….”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挥着拳头，喊着各种可怕的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，门开了，黑雨大王跺着脚走了出来：“你太粗鲁了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还很强大！” 悟空挥动金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！黑雨大王消失了，留下一滩水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈！” 悟空笑了，“一下就死了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挥着金箍棒跑进山洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227283</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 小妖们大叫着跑出了山洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227283</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空找到了师父和悟净，帮他们解开绳子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空，谢谢你！” 唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没事儿，师父！” 悟空看了看四周，“八戒呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净很惊讶：“你没看见八戒吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挣开了绳子，去找妖怪了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他不在山洞里。” 悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧摇了摇头：“八戒一直抱怨很饿，他可能去找吃的了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净皱了皱眉：“八戒怎么能不管我们就走了！太糟糕了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空也摇了摇头：“八戒有时候真是该打！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，悟空听到了脚步声，他看到了一个正要逃跑的迅翼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空迅速跳到迅翼的面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>迅翼后退了几步：“求求你不要伤害我，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我知道猪八戒在哪儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>